        History
        ========
        
        0.2.0 (2012-06-02)
        -------------------
        * Add optional argument for quantity to get_note_list()
        * catch HTTPError when fetching notes
        * immediately return if note could not be fetched
        * trash_note has to succeed for deleting
        * add json import fallbacks
        
